{"id": "1186101906947440750", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "1185814596448165981", "author_name": "c10h16o_1001", "author_bot": false, "content": "确实感觉有点混乱所以想问问，开头的影片说几百年前发现了融蚀然后人们开始研究对策，我还以为那个时候就是洛夫克拉夫特20世纪左右，然后剧情主时间轴是未来……", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T00:25:31.324000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["926498195226370048"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1185929072396730428", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186102117535072339", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185814596448165981", "author_name": "c10h16o_1001", "author_bot": false, "content": "不知道会不会有因为融蚀作怪所以科技经济社会发展都停滞不前的设定", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T00:26:21.532000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186109468673593477", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "应该不会是在未来，发现了融蚀开始研究对策的话应该不会忽略掉融蚀对于社会发展的影响", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T00:55:34.180000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186109814317789194", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "融蚀必然会影响到发展，但有意识地关注下不至于几百年发展停滞不前吧", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T00:56:56.588000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-12-18T00:58:41.026000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186111778598420501", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "除非融蚀比想象中还要强大，开场动画里似乎有说到人们开始研究对策但对融蚀几乎无用", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:04:44.909000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186112385417744495", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "我在想，要是融蚀是有自我意识的话会不会在被发现能够对记忆造成影响的时候就隐藏自己了", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:07:09.586000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186112898628599818", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "然后有意识地将感染约束在同一地区，而不是随机感染或无条件感染遇上的所有人", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:09:11.945000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186113863977017444", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "当某个地区融蚀现象过于强烈的话甚至能让人们把对该地区的所有记忆都抹除掉，或者开启融蚀裂隙将该区域吞噬掉并抹除存在，让人们根本不记得有这么一个地方", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:13:02.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186114267418742794", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "这样的话社会发展受创也不会有人发现到了", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:14:38.290000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186114987639443466", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "这也能解释为何融蚀最近才发现有抹除记忆的现象，而很久以前有一项这样的报告却一直到现在都没有再发现过如此现象", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:17:30.004000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186115522148978761", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "至于为何现在融蚀“不安分”地让这现象展现在调查局面前了...也许是融蚀总攻的前兆了...？", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:19:37.441000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186115907748122775", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "愿银钥指引我们前行", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:21:09.375000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186116692993134592", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "（以上一切纯属脑洞大开）", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T01:24:16.592000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186185426646601768", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "可能世界發展因為融蝕而被帶歪了一部分吧。融蝕很難預防而且就像劇情所說一樣不好追查，對世界發展來說確實是負面的。", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T05:57:23.972000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186185747632504883", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "現在的不安分我覺得也有那些藏在黑暗中蠢蠢欲動的幾個勢力的推動，提燈教會也好雕塑家協會也好，這些上浮並登場的勢力不過是冰山一角罷了。", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T05:58:40.501000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186186650812956723", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後我記得第二章劇情有提到赫伯特的研究，他仍是彌薩格大學研究人員的時候提出過融蝕最終會抹消一個人的存在之類的論點，但那跟劇情提起他這個言論並印證的時間點已經隔了兩三百年。\n可能這部分真的因為融蝕的緣故而難以察覺吧。", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T06:02:15.836000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186237778258821120", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185814596448165981", "author_name": "c10h16o_1001", "author_bot": false, "content": "萝坦的语音里说融蚀出现可比人类意识到想象中早太多了，而她年纪又那么大（嗯？）应该是真的对人类来说很难察觉到这种现象，搞不好其实是自古以来一直都有，然后因为一些势力逐渐爆发了", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T09:25:25.569000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186237982349471764", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185814596448165981", "author_name": "c10h16o_1001", "author_bot": false, "content": "顺便吐槽一下现如今不失忆是没法当手游主角了吗（。", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T09:26:14.228000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186239547512729690", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "可能还要扯到文明起源，世界诞生的秘密啥的，文明出现就是为了对抗融蚀，融蚀可能是在星球诞生那段世纪就冒出来了（萝坦是星球诞生之际就出现了）", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T09:32:27.392000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-12-18T09:32:33.825000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186239913411223604", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "融蚀是星球之敌、神明到来就是为了阻止再一星球遭融蚀抹消啥的", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T09:33:54.629000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186240801525743686", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "甚至可能是神明到来时被带着过来也说不准：被融蚀逼到离开原本的星球 融蚀潜藏在神明身上跟过来了、要么阴谋论这是神明特意带来的：做实验，看上地球的某样东西啥的", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T09:37:26.372000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186240901790584922", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "（脑洞越来越大）", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T09:37:50.277000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186257623671111760", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "點名一款四個字的遊戲（不對）", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T10:44:17.084000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1185814596448165981"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1186237982349471764", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186258040928878642", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "融蝕也可能是到了某個時候才因為某些疏忽或是裂縫跑進來的，或者，在地球上出現時間比想像中更早，但人們真正能感受到它大規模活躍並且可供紀錄的時間很晚", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T10:45:56.566000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186261197763399680", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過說到底，現在才剛開始呢，就像跑團才調查了個開頭，後面到底還有什麼都難說。等待並心懷希望吧。（雙手合十）", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T10:58:29.214000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186268928792600636", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "因为有记忆的话一切谜底就揭晓了？😆", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T11:29:12.435000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186268983427600466", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "~~没法水剧情了~~", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T11:29:25.461000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186272439014019172", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "有記憶就等於有人設有過去吧，這樣在寫的時候可能也會引起爭議（？）最好的方式就是失憶規避", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T11:43:09.337000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186277604639113216", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "有记忆应该也不会对人设造成影响。人设部分主要是看剧情文本怎么写，记忆最多也就回顾重要的时间片段，而影响人设的心理活动和生理行为被文本决定", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T12:03:40.918000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186284748797128734", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "712663356032680007", "author_name": "scarlet_t07", "author_bot": false, "content": "总结就是人物被刀不是因为守密人太懵懂啥事都来不及做，而是作者想发🔪", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T12:32:04.218000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186287289500979231", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "一個寫文的想發刀子就跟跑團被撕卡一樣攔不住（樂", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T12:42:09.969000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186288018131263529", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實還有一種可能就是設定的沒失憶前的逼格太高，寫文的寫不出來（有感）", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T12:45:03.688000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186297765597294652", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "一般主角會設定成失憶或菜鳥其實是為了使玩家更好的代入主角的視角，以及更好帶出新手教學這個流程的合理性（", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T13:23:47.665000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-12-18T13:24:02.921000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186298505170534480", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "590172023112597558", "author_name": "xill42", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以如果有個遊戲主角沒失憶也不是菜鳥卻還是不會\n是不是就會被旁邊陪同的人表示：你是怎麼當上這個位置的", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T13:26:43.993000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["777861907973406731"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1186297765597294652", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1186298605468917821", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且要是主角一上來在劇情裡就是不可能失敗的滿級大佬那玩家要是玩得很爛不就挺不合理", "timestamp": "2023-12-18T13:27:07.906000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
